HEADWORD: Wiring
<hw>Wir"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
one that wires anything.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The wires or conductors employed in any system in
which electric voltages or current are transmitted between
components.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wiry</ent>⟦br⟧
